g und Frieden\r\n- Kontakte zwischen den Menschen unserer Länder\r\n- Freiheit, Vielfalt und den Respekt anderer Kulturen\r\n- Austausch zwischen Deutschland und Frankreich und weiteren Partnern\r\n- unsere gemeinsamen europäischen Werte und\r\n- ein vereintes Europa","activityOperationType":"SELF_OPERATED","clientOrganizations":[],"clientPersons":[],"codexViolation":false,"disclosureRequirementsExist":false,"donationInformationRequired":false,"donators":[],"employeeCount":{"from":0,"to":0},"fieldsOfInterest":[{"code":"FOI_CULTURE","de":"Kultur","en":"Culture"},{"code":"FOI_EDUCATION_PARENTING","de":"Bildung und Erziehung","en":"Education and parenting"},{"code":"FOI_EDUCATION_PARENTING|FOI_EP_ACADEMIC","de":"Hochschulbildung","en":"Academic education"},{"code":"FOI_EDUCATION_PARENTING|FOI_EP_CHILDHOOD","de":"Vorschulische Bildung","en":"Early childhood education"},{"code":"FOI_EDUCATION_PARENTING|FOI_EP_OTHER","de":"Sonstiges im Bereich „Bildung und Erziehung“","en":"Other in the field of “Education and parenting”"},{"code":"FOI_EDUCATION_PARENTING|FOI_EP_SCHOOL","de":"Schulische Bildung","en":"School education"},{"code":"FOI_EDUCATION_PARENTING|FOI_EP_WORK","de":"Berufliche Bildung","en":"Job education"},{"code":"FOI_EUROPEAN_UNION|FOI_EU_LAWS","de":"EU-Gesetzgebung","en":"EU legislation"},{"code":"FOI_EUROPEAN_UNION|FOI_EU_OTHER","de":"Sonstiges im Bereich „Europapolitik und Europäische Union“","en":"Other in the field of “European politics and the EU”"},{"code":"FOI_EUROPEAN_UNION|FOI_EU_POLITICS","de":"Institutionelle Fragen der EU","en":"Institutional questions of European politics"},{"code":"FOI_EUROPEAN_UNION","de":"Europapolitik und Europäische Union","en":"European politics and the EU"},{"code":"FOI_FOREIGN_AFFAIRS|FOI_FA_CULTURE","de":"Auswärtige Kultur- und Bildungspolitik","en":"Foreign cultural and educational policy"},{"code":"FOI_FOREIGN_AFFAIRS|FOI_FA_INTERNATIONAL","de":"Internationale Beziehungen","en":"International relations"},{"code":"FOI_FOREI